profile_positions.description:
Freelance consultant for the Training of Trainers Project. Tasks include:
1) Rewriting training documents including the Guide for Trainers on Health Promotion and Behaviour Change;
2) Development of four e-learning modules: 1. Meaningful Youth Participation, 2. Measurement on an Outcome Level,3.Health Promotion and Behaviour, 4. Data analysis;
3) Improving and add relevant training materials, such as factsheets on meaningful youth participation, promotion of condom-use in faith-based organisations and advocacy of sexual diversity (LGBTI).
4) Co-facilitator of SRHR training in Uganda and South-Africa (planned for Sept. 2014) on research and data analysis.
